mono<T> and flux<T> are 2 data types
mono return single object and flux returns multiple objects

Its a pub sub model
    subscriber -> subscribe() -> publisher -> Subscription() to subscriber
    Then subscriber makes request() and publisher calls onnext() of subscriber multiple times to send data
    Then publisher send calls onComplete